N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4025.26 - Omission by vendor to strike out

State Regulations

Omission by the vendor to strike a horse out of an
engagement, not sold or transferred with the horse, does not entitle such
horse's owner to start the horse or to the stakes if such horse
wins. Notes
